summary: This cable discusses the potential hazard of UNSKAPU/9 firing to AMLASH/1 and suggests methods to determine the background of UNSNAFU/19's statement about U/9 being a "dirty KUBARK agent." It proposes using AMWHIP/1 and his jeweler friend in Havana, Jose Iglesias, to relay information to ANLASH/1.
title: DIR 95504: UNSKAPU/9 Firing and Potential Hazard to AMLASH/1
